{"tid":1740020,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"彌敦道每晚啲路障原來係佢地清","createTime":"2019-11-19T21:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T23:13:38.000Z","uid":10268,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a9be6427a70756cc91fcdceaeaa18425e6ed6fd7","tid":1740020,"uid":10268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:48:06.000Z","msg":"小弟返夜啱啱彌敦道附近收工<br />\n見到手足整既路障好爽<br />\n去到山東街果頭見到啲勁黑既人係馬路<br />\n以為仲有手足<br />\n行近睇原來全部都係狗<br />\n佢地清晨係度逐舊逐舊磚執返埋路邊<br />\n我行入西洋菜街走<br />\n見到成個十字頭路口都仲有磚<br />\n心諗你班狗就好<br />\n執磚都有十皮一個月<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外 我見旺角無磚既路打哂石屎地<br />\n要留心返之後可能旺角無得玩磚<br />\n要諗一諗其他路障<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光時"},{"pid":"19b9a35a43b4623b3f6c89a2b64dea536f9243e5","tid":1740020,"uid":144522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T22:53:24.000Z","msg":"光時<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8627aaf39d2b761b5a0d36c0285acc0fbecc532e","tid":1740020,"uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T23:06:29.000Z","msg":"等佢執完一腳掃番出去<br />\n光時<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373f2687cfc2b65f31e6bc0e1a5b4961c0e1cbdf","tid":1740020,"uid":24332,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T23:13:38.000Z","msg":"屌你老味啲磚頭唔要撚就<br />\n彌敦道要隨時走嘅戰區班少爺兵係逃生路線放磚玩鳩手足<br />\n彌敦道唔同city歌和老街 咪撚見入地擺完有人影相放ig就照做啊屌 玩撚死人㗎"}]}